#Hangman Game (Python)

A simple Python program that allows you to play the classic Hangman game.
Guess the letters of a randomly selected word before you run out of lives!

#Features

Random word selection from a predefined word list (hangman_words.py)

Visual Hangman stages (hangman_art.py) showing your remaining lives

Tracks correct and incorrect guesses

Game ends when all letters are guessed or lives reach zero

Clean and simple Python code structure


#How It Works

Run the program

Input:

Guess one letter at a time

The program:

Randomly selects a word from the word list

Displays _ placeholders for unguessed letters

Updates the display with correct guesses

Decreases lives for incorrect guesses and shows hangman stages

Ends the game with a win if all letters are guessed, or a loss if lives reach zero
  
